[ETAPES 1:]

[install minikube]

1) install virtual box (msc)
2) brew install kubernetes-cli
3) chmod +x ./kubectl
4) brew install minikube
5) minikube start --vm-driver=virtualbox       # rm -rf ~/.minikube  ==> nettoyer  # minikube delete => supprimer cluster local
6) kubectl config use-context minikube          # pas obligatoire (automatique)



minikube start
minikube addons enable dashboard # 